No. 602,

Misc.

Chaapel v. Cochran, Corrections Director.

This motion for leave to file an application for a writ of habeas corpus is hereby transferred “for hearing and determination” to the United States District Court for the Southern District of Florida. 28 U. S. C. § 2241 (b); Rule 31 (5), Revised Rules of the Supreme Court of the United States (1954); Ex parte Abernathy, 320 U. S. 219.

Mr. Justice White took no part in the consideration or disposition of this motion.
